   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Öthe present month... Öhaving given bail to Sokomenis, the warden, to release me in light of the circumstances. But Sokomenis, after receiving two bail payments from me, is not acting in good faith. I am asking that, if you agree, to the extent that you take the matter in hand and bring it to a head (?), you not overlook me, who has wasted away 8 months and been disdained by the... Önot managing well the things in their control and belonging to others, but things relating to consumption tax (?)... Öand if he should appearÖof the bail paymentsÖrelease meÖI may be able in light of the circumstancesÖ.</ab>
